                                <item text-type="text/html">&lt;span style="font-style: normal;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: normal;"&gt;The action is blocked and the document &lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;Status&lt;/span&gt; cannot be changed.&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;</item>
